{#
NovaSight Datasource Transformation DAG Template
=================================================

Generates an Airflow DAG for running dbt transformations
for a specific data source after ingestion completes.

Template Variables:
- tenant_id: str - Tenant identifier (required)
- datasource_id: str - Data source identifier
- datasource_name: str - Normalized data source name
- dag_id: str - DAG identifier
- ingestion_dag_id: str - Upstream ingestion DAG to wait for
- schedule: str - Cron expression or preset
- tasks: List[Dict] - Task configurations
- run_tests: bool - Whether to run dbt tests
- dbt_project_dir: str - Path to dbt project
- dbt_profiles_dir: str - Path to dbt profiles
- dbt_target: str - dbt target environment

Template Version: {{ _template_version | default('1.0.0') }}
